# Template Rules

## Principles
- Templates are canonical; improve them instead of forking.
- Keep placeholders explicit: `{{title}}`, `{{date}}`.
- Include frontmatter stubs and Related Notes sections.

## Compatibility
- Templates must work with Templater/core Templates plugin patterns.
- Stay conceptually aligned with `docs/templates/` for website publishing.

## When Adding a Template
1. Add file under `knowledgeos/22-Templates/`
2. Link from [[Templates Index]]
3. Mention intended domain and ID scheme if applicable
